import React,{useState} from 'react'

const Search = () => {
    return (
        <section className='search'>
        <form>
            <input 
            type='text'
             className='form-control'
              placeholder='Search Character'
               autoFocus>  
               </input>
        </form>
            
        </section>
    )
}

export default Search
